      "highlight_excellence": "Excellence in ethics: Recognizing when a 'surgical cure' is not possible and focusing on airway protection.",
      "address_gaps": "Address the poor 1-year survival rate (<20%).",
      "review_learning_points": "Aggressive oncological emergency.",
