      "highlight_excellence": "Localization with Sestamibi scan and Ultrasound allows for minimally invasive parathyroidectomy.",
      "address_gaps": "Address 'hungry bone syndrome' as a post-operative risk (severe hypocalcemia).",
      "review_learning_points": "Common endocrine surgical condition.",
      "plan": "Check 24-hour urine calcium to rule out Familial Hypocalciuric Hypercalcemia (FHH) before surgery."
