      "highlight_excellence": "Recognizing that 'H\u00fcrthle cell adenoma' cannot be distinguished from 'carcinoma' by FNA alone; needs a formal lobe excision.",
      "address_gaps": "Identify the abundance of mitochondria as the cause of the granular 'oxyphilic' cytoplasm.",
      "review_learning_points": "Thyroid pathology board topic.",
